   <body>
      <ol>
         <li>
            <p>Inspect all wear elements at regular intervals for wear and damage. Replace if
               necessary. Otherwise, serious damage to the mixer may result.</p>
            <p>
               <ul>
                  <li>The wear limit is reached when the screw heads are level with the wear
                     liner.</li>
                  <li>Wear liners must be replaced when this wear limit is reached.</li>
               </ul>
               <p>
                  <fig id="fig_awl_dks_lcc">
                     <image href="media/image2.jpg"
                            placement="break"
                            id="image_bwl_dks_lcc"
                            align="center"/>
