                     </p>
                  </fig>
               </p>
            </p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Replacing steel sheet inner wall liner segments:</p>
            <p>
               <ul>
                  <li>Detach the old inner wall segments by grinding off the tack welds on the joints
                     of the inner wall segments and central section. </li>
                  <li>Remove the old inner wall segments.</li>
                  <li>Align the new inner wall segments with the inner wall.</li>
                  <li>Tack weld together at the joints with short weld seams.</li>
               </ul>
               <p>
                  <fig id="fig_t1t_lks_lcc">
                     <image href="media/image3.jpg"
                            placement="break"
                            id="image_u1t_lks_lcc"
