                  </fig>
               </p>
            </p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Replacing steel sheet or hard cast iron floor liner segments (wear
               plates):</p>
            <p>Remove the bottom parts for one or two of the mixing arms. Refer to Section 2,
               step 2 above.<ul id="ul_xnn_zks_lcc">
                  <li>Remove the screws (3, 4), and remove the threaded plate (1).</li>
                  <li>The arm should be free.</li>
               </ul>
               <note type="note" id="note_ynn_zks_lcc">
                  <p>Re-tighten the connections between the top part of the mixing arm and the
                     bottom part of the mixing arm after 5 hours of operating time.</p>
               </note>
               <p>
                  <fig id="fig_znn_zks_lcc">
                     <image href="media/image4.jpg"
                            placement="break"
                            id="image_a4n_zks_lcc"
