                           </entry>
                        </row>
                     </tbody>
                  </tgroup>
               </table>
            </note>
            <p>Assembling the wear sleeves:</p>
            <p>
               <ul>
                  <li>Press the rubber or PUR wear sleeves (2) over the mixing arms (1) from the
                     front, directly above the mixing paddles (3).</li>
                  <li>Secure them in the rear by turning in the retainers integrated into the
                     sleeve.</li>
                  <li>Use tack welds to additionally secure the steel or special cast metal wear
                     sleeves (with the appropriate electrodes).</li>
               </ul>
